	"event.arrangement.k.1": "@, thank you for coming to the sewers. It's much more comfortable for all of us monsters here.$1",
	"event.arrangement.w.1": "Please be aware that they have taken a great leap of faith being here today.",
	"event.arrangement.k.2": "My friends are just over here, follow me...",
	"event.arrangement.k.3": "@, we are offering an arrangement.",
	"event.arrangement.k.4": "There are those of us who wish to find refuge on your farm.#$b#The Wizard will help you build a sanctuary for them. In exchange, the monsters who reside in the sanctuary#$b#will produce treasures that their people find the most valuable.",
	"event.arrangement.w.2": "I have developed the blueprints for the Monster Sanctuary and sent them to Robin,#$b#though she doesn't know the building's true purpose...#$b#she believes it is simply a mine entrance with an upgraded cask area for more wine production.",
	"event.arrangement.k.5": "*chuckle*",
	"event.arrangement.w.3": "*chuckle*",
	"event.arrangement.w.4": "I will also teach you how to summon the monsters safely and discreetly to their new home.#$b#We must not worry the townsfolk. Here.",
	"event.arrangement.m.1": "{{PlayerName}} has learned how to make the Summoning Circle.",
	"event.arrangement.k.6": "I look forward to seeing our friendships between our peoples grow. Safety from such...unpleasant encounters...it means more than you know.",

/*
 ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ  ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ               ‚Ėą‚Ėą     ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ     
 ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą               ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ     ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚Ėą     
 ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   ‚ĖĄ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĄ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą       ‚Ėą‚Ėą     
 ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą   ‚ĖÄ ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚Ėą‚Ėą     ‚Ėą‚Ėą       ‚Ėą‚Ėą     
 ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚Ėą  ‚ĖĄ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚Ėą     ‚Ėą‚Ėą       ‚Ėą‚Ėą     
 ‚Ėą‚Ėą    ‚Ėą‚Ėą  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą  ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ    ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ  
 ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ    ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ   ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ  ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ     ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ  
Mail
*/
	"mail.krobus.title.1": "Krobus' Curiosity",
	"mail.krobus.body.1": "Mysterious Newcomer,^^I have seen you start your journey underground... I wonder if you will be like the others...^^Not all are like the ones of us you have already encountered in the mines. I hope to meet you in the sewers. Please do not take too long...^^-Krobus",
	"mail.krobus.title.2": "A Monster's Choice",
	"mail.krobus.body.2": "@,^^You have already caused quite the stir deep underground. Fear has begun to creep into the Shadow People's and other monsters' hearts. But there are those of us who believe you might be different? That you might delight in the same treasure we do...^^-Krobus",
	"mail.krobus.title.3": "Rings of Friendship",
	"mail.krobus.body.3": "@,^^I have spoken to some other creatures who live in the dark. We wish to offer you a proposal...^^We will teach you how to craft magnificent rings that will signify to others in the dark that you are friendly and wish to not fight. We offer these three recipes to you in hopes that a peace between us can begin.^^You will need to grow in your knowledge by mining in the depths. I will be able to teach you about more rings as you grow in skill... for a price. ^^-Krobus",
	"mail.krobus.title.4": "A Mysterious Meeting",
	"mail.krobus.body.4": "@,^^Please come to the sewers at your earliest convenience. There is something I would like to speak to you about.^^-Krobus",
	"mail.krobus.title.5": "One Ring for Them All",
	"mail.krobus.body.5": "@,^^Those of us who dwell underground are very happy with the progress we have seen. You have proven to every different monster people who reside in the Pelican Town Mines that you are willing to coexist and even delight in our treasures the same way we do.^^We have decided to share with you how to craft a very powerful magical ring. This is the combination of all of our peoples' knowledge.^^Thank you,^Krobus",
}